<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-538-662  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 538 662.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Digital Review  June 4 1990 v7 n22 p14(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Cahners-Ziff Publishing Associates LP 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Lex word processor gains All-in-1, Oracle interfaces. (TrajectorySoftware introduces Lex 9C word processor) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Ballou, Melinda-Carol.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Trajectory Software Inc. (product introduction).andO;Product:   Lex 9C (Word processing software) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     Interprocess CommunicationWord Processing SoftwareProduct IntroductionRelational DBMS.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Lex word processor gains All-in-1, Oracle interfacesandM;RIDGEWOOD, N.J.andP;  -- Trajectory Software has released a version of its Lexword processing software that offers interfaces to All-in-1 and Oracle'sRDBMS.andM;&quot;Anybody using Oracle can access information from Lex to either callinformation into Lex documents or to access it directly,&quot; said Al Bracco,Trajectory's president.andM;Other features in Lex version 9C include a 160,000-word thesaurus, pop-uphelp windows, on-screen line and box drawing, LaserJet proportional fonts andPostScript support, company officials said.andM;Lex's spell checker has been made fully interactive and the dictionary hasbeen enlarged to 175,000 words, they added.andM;The company also offers spreadsheet and graphics modules with Lex 9C.andM;This release of Lex will be demonstrated at Booth 126 at the Dexpo East showthis month in Boston.andM;Prices for Lex on VMS and DOS range from $395 to $20,000, and versions forUltrix, Unix and Xenix will be available by the end of October.andP;  Prices forthe graphics and spreadsheet modules range from $495 to $15,000.andM;The interfaces to Oracle and All-in-1 are priced from $295 to $5,000.andM;Bracco added that the company plans to offer support for Ingres, then Rdb andInformix, within a year.andP;  &quot;We're in the early stages now,&quot; he said.andP;  &quot;We alsojust started work on an X windows port.&quot;andM;Trajectory Software Inc. can be contacted at 555 Goffle Road, Ridgewood, NJ07450, (800) 445-9292; (201) 447-5656.andO;</TEXT></DOC>